<h3>Tips for students to prepare for the SLEP test and to practice English skills:</h3>
<ol>
<li>Read the Book of Mormon in English everyday.</li>
<li>Get basic English grammar books and review exercises therein.</li>
<li>Practice as much as you can with missionaries and English speakers.</li>
<li>Watch movies in English and listen to songs, paying attention to the words.</li>
<li>Pray for the Lord's help.</li>
</ol>
